devdoc.author: edsphinx
devdoc.details: This contract creates individual escrow vaults (`CommitmentVault`) for securing RWA NFTs, such as tokenized access to clinical trials.

createCommitmentVault(uint256,address,ui.details: Verifies that the interaction's compliance level is 2 or higher. The caller must be a participant in the interaction and the owner of the RWA NFT.

params._experienceNFTAddress: The address of the RWA NFT contract (e.g., Trial Access Token).
params._experienceTokenId: The ID of the specific RWA NFT to be escrowed.
params._matchId: The ID of the on-chain interaction (e.g., a verified clinical visit).

devdoc.title: Commitment Vault Factory

createCommitmentVault(uint256,address,ui.notice: Creates a Commitment Vault for a specific on-chain interaction.

userdoc.notice: A factory contract that allows participants to create their own Commitment Vaults.
